name: Parccoun - An Unfinished Game Off Game
name_original: Parccoun - An Unfinished Game Off Game
description:
You play a Raccoon who has stumbled upon an old TV with someone's favorite 8-bit parkour game. Let's see how fast you can do one of the following:

  • Find the end of the levels
  • Find a bug
  • Find the ratings and comments section of this jam page to tell me what you think about what you did play

Thanks for stopping by
